data.description: LOCATION! Welcome home to this beautiful, Oversized Ranch located in an incredible school district. This stunning 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home sits on a gorgeous, landscaped, 1 acre lot in the River Elan subdivision - one of the only homes in the neighborhood with this size lot! This natural light-filled, open-concept home features a spacious primary suite on the main floor, his and her closets, double vanity, and separate shower and bathtub. Separate Dining Room and Vaulted family room with Gas burning fireplace which makes for a peaceful evening. The Kitchen features breakfast bar and breakfast area. Walk out onto the huge Private Patio off the kitchen with view of a waterfall leading to Koi pond and an additional deck overlooking the beautiful, private yard. The Guest suite is located upstairs with 1/2 bath and Kitchenette. EZ care landscaping with sprinkler system. NO HOA - making this a perfect AirBnB, VRBO, or Rental Property. This home is situated in the most convenient location. Extremely close to Lake Lanier, Chateau Elon Vineyard and Golf Course, 10 minutes from Michelin Raceway Road Atlanta, Mall of Georgia, Restaurants, and much more! Owner motivated. Within 10 minutes of Michelin Raceway Road Atlanta! This home will make for a killer investment! This home will not last long! Several photos in this listing have been virtually staged.
